use case : use case diagram wich is represent user activity with system {ye ek drawing hoti hai}

     in this use case diagram ther are there are 3 mai sections
(1) actor : wich is represent actor or user of the system {kon user hai (actor)}
(2) activity : wich is represent by oval symbol - wich represent activity perform by respective user or actor{isme user or actor ka kam suru se and tak kesa hoga vo pta chalta hai}
(3) system : wich is sarounded by reactangle baorders{system ke ander kya kya part hai}